<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>A drone carrying prescription drugs and other contraband was found near Long Bay jail earlier this year.</p>

<p>Police say a member of the public found the drone on June 7 on the road on Zion Avenue at Malabar, and took it to Maroubra Police Station.</p>

<p>Long Bay jail, a maximum and minimum security prison is located on a 32 hectare site at Malabar.</p>

<p>A drone carrying prescription drugs and other contraband was found near Long Bay jail earlier this year</p>

<p>Police say the package attached to the drone was found to contain buprenorphine, a SIM card and other electronic items.</p>

<p>Officers from Eastern Beaches Police Area Command began an investigation into the location of the drone and prescription drugs.</p>

<p>Detectives have released CCTV vision of two men and are appealing for anyone with information about their identities to come forward.</p>

<p>Police have also released an image of the drone located at Malabar.</p>
